author: Benedict Correya
text:
Nice and clean gym with well-maintained equipment and a good variety for different workouts. The space feels comfortable and not too crowded.
One thing that could make the experience even better would be having a water dispenser inside the gym. Overall, a great place to work out in Tengah.

author: Jovan Lau Yong Khang
text: The gym at Tengah Anytime Fitness is spacious and well-equipped with a wide variety of machines and equipment to suit all fitness levels. They offer plenty of classes and have a strong, supportive community where members encourage and motivate each other. A special shoutout to the manager, Iskandar, and the personal trainers ‚Äî they are always helpful and approachable. Highly recommend this gym to anyone looking for a positive and energetic environment to work out!

author: Lau Guan Zhen (Sean)
text:
Anytime Fitness Tengah is a fantastic gym with all the amenities you need for a great workout experience! The gym is spacious, well-equipped, and spotlessly clean, with a wide variety of machines and free weights for every fitness level. Whether you‚Äôre into cardio, strength training, or functional exercises, they have it all.

The staff is friendly and professional, always ready to assist with any questions or provide guidance. There‚Äôs also 24/7 access, which is perfect for those with a flexible schedule. Plus, the atmosphere is welcoming and not intimidating, making it a great place for beginners as well as experienced gym-goers.

The facility also has clean changing rooms and showers, and there‚Äôs plenty of parking available nearby. Overall, a top-notch gym in a convenient location‚Äîdefinitely worth checking out!

text:

author: Jairaj Jeyabal
text:
This is definitely one of the best gyms in the west. Amazing layout, really spacious, fantastic selection of equipment. A good range of free weights & plate loaded machines for those who like to lift heavy and an equally good variety of cable machines, functional equipment and cardio.

The staff are very friendly & helpful and I love the positive vibes and energy that they bring to this place. Highly recommended! I'm definitely going to make my trips to Tengah a weekly affair.

author: yatassha abdul fattah (yatassha)
text: Absolutely love working out at Tengah Anytime Fitness! The classes are always fun and engaging, and the gym is consistently clean and well-maintained. The staff are incredibly jovial, helpful, and full of positive energy ‚Äî they never fail to hype us up, especially as newbies just starting our fitness journey. Even after a long day, at 9pm, they still have the energy to cheer us on and keep the vibe alive. Their dedication, patience, and warm encouragement make all the difference. Thank you for making fitness feel fun and achievable!

author: Huishan Lan
text:
Joining Anytime Fitness Tengah was one of my best decisions in life! It sounds like I‚Äôm exaggerating but honestly, I have joined other gyms in the past and the environment and vibes just didn‚Äôt make me feel motivated to continue, and others are just way too expensive.

Conversely, Anytime Fitness Tengah was super affordable and they offered a really clean and great environment - new machines, cool air-con, well-maintained cleanliness (I see cleaners doing their work all the time when I workout) and they have the most fun and bubbly team ever.

The full-time staff are all very friendly and motivating, and would often give good advice and explain concepts to help me achieve my fitness goals, even though I did not sign up for PT sessions. Even the intern was very helpful (he even demonstrated for me to see) when I approached him to explain to me about the machine that I have not tried before and he was there to make sure I was doing it right.

Recently, AF Tengah introduced group classes and we‚Äôve formed a really supportive community where no one judges our fitness levels so it‚Äôs really just all of us having good fun working out together!

I never knew ‚Äúsuffering‚Äù could feel this good! ü§≠

author: Cookie C
text: AF tengah equipment and space are clean and neat. Staffs on duty are always friendly and smile to greet everytime I went. Classes are also interesting. Glad that it's so convenient for tengah residents.

author: Nicole Hiu
text: ive been loving this gym ever since it opened ! the staff never failed to check in regularly to ask how things can be improved , and never failed to greet us. equipments are all new and while the space is not huge , i find that theres everything i need for my workouts :) again , special shoutout to the staff who never failed to make my siblings and i laugh for all the silly classes we took part in LOL it really helped to make us feel welcomed , and made the gym a lot less intimidating ü•π

author: Lee Poh Ling
text: Got the call from club manager Caroline and she is making everything smooth n I m pretty happy and I wish to have good start and good memory with this gym with my partner. Happy exercise!!!

author: h r
text:
AF Tengah is new with a small squarish layout. The equipment selection are very basic due to the size of the space. Becos of that, when the Tengah crowd comes in progressively, with more BTO around the estate getting ready, the whole gym may feel very packed easily.

Its hard for AF Tengah to convert more fitness enthu members from nearby gyms with better equipment. Eg, AF Tengah only has 2 power racks compared to AF Bukit Batok with 6 power racks. Probably can only attract people who stay in Tengah for convenience but dont drive.

Management may need to think ahead and reconfigure the equipment within the small unit to spread out the crowd in future. The loose furniture and resting area seems like taking a portion of the unit which may not be needed since the gym is in a residential area. For consideration please.

author: Wen Liueh Kueh
text: One of the better branches with new equipments.. Except some of the machines need getting used to cause the latches can be a bit difficult to maneuver. Spacious and the temperature is nicely controlled. The machines can be quite close to each other so be careful when you walk between them when trying to stack your weights
